mation Systems）</li>	<li>国际贸易（International Business）</li>	<li>市场营销（Marketing）</li>	<li>战略与创业管理（Strategy &amp; Entrepreneurship）</li>	<li>运筹学（Operations Management）</li>	<li>物流管理（Supply Chain Management）*(13)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=QrzUA2XCk3Fezdw_1lPo4EYmU2qOhmfY4buTGFCNmWPgoT7c831R8nyx_O_SBgO1RFsUGJl1hbepC7c6dEPcuUoChx3TqpC7x8adn21PddcTxHJ' target='_blank'>PhD Admissions</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8veOzkc7SCZQheeeeeuSSTGWoOGVrjZdkt75mLFzTe_DrqSeucq7ubl7EGPN9wjSdesb2igwhHyzdPT_iPt5-6_Q-Dxl8uYFBkc4iOhVO3hgKDOSiKQS_W7--bszSNVU6hboe' target='_blank'>Applications</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWP7wzOaRiU9OC-fdZOthaGfFJH1fOOHJ08t1Evs7p2Og14zPDWhgWFFawM8go-FewjeZQsbFAa3yMcjf11AWwWugj14vO-piWzB1iQj4bFWFZa4' target='_blank'>ENGLISH PROFICIENCY REQUIREMENT FOR ADMISSION</a>UIUC</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlZywRjyJFesccccccGiSJruZ2dOLTDO_caEumO-i4OTe4HNm8AIT0D7z7qxz7vE6i4ku-UGnot0hIkD745Zus2oHmDM7Zd' target='_blank'>Oral English Proficiency Testing</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9Mj-jL5VUFpwxooooo5nJz6PNzLBKXZsM0WwF7-tENXAF7VcF7-ZFNXAk2zPhz86QV75T9cF7pei3pji3WviApe80tL5T4v8osC8TpOiAp3FTrq4vb' target='_blank'>Fees</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(6)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=DroIGDO1LSONzbLxai7Ro9SNTPNZpLbwXrH4QjXyr7pp7z6gDSDJ-3i9KrSD1FRwvJraQPsKsrAnaSUE2qhdman3najhgnrutqkeXCVqZ6wGu2KgwUusxdUA9hiWCADCr' target='_blank'>Admissions</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(7)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=frh1ZEb1LSONzHR3pppppEbUQH2SQ1z_9c7uZRiJvdmS9jiJofiJvciS9jONQAkNvOTn6jINwcqSw-Z9N-u3NXZHJVmhyO63J0WEP-0_VyLqXh0ldhievM0q3-' target='_blank'>Deadlines</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(8)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redire