和RA一般的补助金额为$17,757（9个月，不含夏季学期）。夏季学期的补助金额为$3,946；2015-2016学年TA和RA一般的补助金额为$18,701.55（9个月，不含夏季学期）。夏季学期的补助金额为$4,155.9*(1)(4)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>天文学专业研究领域：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7pCwBdbNx6MHHHHHHtWyVJWYuBzPnpYpYraLYWLdt-t2nGITLkIBUkm_Hgb0CDM0xAnJmvDlIml2j3tcjtBNWr5okf' target='_blank'>Research Programs</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=PrgaXqFBwCpmLKBI111111oFYZBVdWEikCkCg3DUIToVjVDAjE5AjvcAboZsmd0fFBwa-dOWCXwag1Y4ZBwDrBlDm1YJLTwmgoYmFTvcF' target='_blank'>GRADUATE APPLICATIONS AND ADMISSIONS-Department of Astronomy</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=pr9ExTHqkW_gBhVxb5U4m-R9ZPq_J8ORVoiTmq2Z_BchlMkTKC3RJOMQ3PU4DhE8jQIPMQpTRD3zRrROcmpqCCLkHZMG3VmmpH1D9MT_g-x_ukdcmjNS' target='_blank'>ENGLISH PROFICIENCY REQUIREMENT FOR ADMISSION</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVdHkp6PZWIeDDDDDDvyR95wG73s0qUHoUmJRqiwCu_aWzY-J7Z-VNvskg4bkNFymAsyqAz09t4w-cnxfteJDuer' target='_blank'>2016-2017 Academic Year Graduate &amp; Professional Tuition Rates</a> UIUC</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbykQkrW5Uk2Koooooo0H-Ce_5qkUGpSpSlTz5pel4lTY4N1Y4H8Y5lT-DB6GLbPRnBrqUSPRECY1MbPOtbKODCYBnahx' target='_blank'>PROSPECTIVE STUDENT FAQ- Department of Astronomy</a> 伊利诺伊大学厄本那-香槟分校</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>大气科学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.7%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.72%">			<p>$26,502</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.42%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:20.08%">			<p>1月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:11.7%">			<p>80</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style=