mospheric Chemistry and Aerosols）</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><ul>	<li>气候研究（Climate Research）	<ul>		<li>气候变化分析与建模（Climate Change Analysis and Modeling）</li>		<li>气候过程与相互作用（Climate Processes and Interactions）</li>		<li>气候变化与综合评估（Integrated Assessment of Climate Change）</li>		<li>天气与气候风险（Weather and Climate Risk）*(8)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>大气科学专业课程设置：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_1kkniNS4P0HAJP68CLUFVUH0_CcbKOxRMtm7rcFpQm5mhrxQ2Y85CcTDBjEcXYMpappe87PVE_JJMoiY0i7WuTV4RpLfqS6aaCYezB7EVhYkwl' target='_blank'>Atmospheric Sciences (ATMS)</a></li>	<li>就业与实习：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_2HwSnOKhLzRF078B1j1Qm3d-cf71kBtFMbzTqn6weDXfj2XaoqUmFSn35Eg4MdBvs0FII0dB3IOtIvkzTqpFxWDSB67HEQJOb1xdKb6ykr1QNGz-zTsBPGxrX-fZzk8k0r9EwB-jnQ4d_cdYzNBvi1' target='_blank'>UNIVERSITY OF ILLINOIS ATMOSPHERIC SCIENCES CAREER CENTER</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=XrChP9xZLDXYcxwxooooo5YJz6PNndhKluP7OZGYIUdsmt7PRirqLF-9g8TI68T9L8okOFT4gausviApMw3XO5osen_wzkM015RIQ1Ew5QZrm5-SsGRINki07dEjy1E4zo-i6YFizf' target='_blank'>ADMISSIONS REQUIREMENTS FOR THE M.S. AND PH.D. DEGREE PROGRAMS</a>UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWA5khMQa0V7jQQeh43Iwq8nXupYN1-CuAIJPMWQvqw_H3_J4cjUIXYQ13hCiSw3tFZL1C3amOzSMjDZLPMWm5QB_SYqxo85OkIR68HZ6_d9CVwaL12NoR1cQXBjkYCVw-t6RvOCgP1L12NoU4_yU97S' target='_blank'>HOW TO APPLY TO THE M.S. OR PH.D. PROGRAM IN ATMOSPHERIC SCIENCES</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkM5ewqQ5MVwkIIIIoqqDgx3Nb_TX5dnxWb_WcTGxK4RJI1aSI1w2I2wCYOPQx3PC8EjXOEuXd56GAgjsam6ZkTWZw' target='_blank'>2016-2017 Academic Year Graduate &amp; Professional Tuition Rates</a> UIUC</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkM5JwaAvy-1VBBBBBkGjPX5lRX9E7ZWo9z9SESlKq2ufEc2uXFBuXY3yWwiX9cQ_r89uUzP4VapD1Zf9bBgPv08sawUOt_k6efdkrwWz7udSe_4OyqEbiSBt8x3tdBna4xfUbQW'