ww.qianmu.org/经济学' target='_blank'>Economics</a>）</li>	<li>农业科学与领导教育（Agricultural Science and Leadership Education）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/动物科学' target='_blank'>动物科学</a>（Department of Animal Sciences）</li>	<li>作物科学（Department of Crop Sciences）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/食品科学' target='_blank'>食品科学</a>与人类营养（Department of Food Science and Human Nutrition）</li>	<li>人类发展与家庭研究（Human Development and Family Studies）</li>	<li>人与社区发展（Department of Human and Community Development）</li>	<li>自然资源与环境（Department of Natural Resources and Environmental Sciences）</li>	<li>营养科学（Nutritional Sciences）</li>	<li>农业传播（Agricultural Communications Program）：开设本科项目</li>	<li>农业教育（Agricultural Education Program）：在线教育项目*(1)(2)(3)(4)</li></ul><p>专业硕士项目</p><ul>	<li>农业生产（Agricultural Production）</li>	<li>生物能源（Bioenergy）</li>	<li>技术系统管理（Technical Systems Management）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/食品科学' target='_blank'>食品科学</a>与人类营养（Department of Food Science and Human Nutrition）*(2)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_2LwolVBYX7ttttttRjPX5lRsDIy35N49wiX5Au39AuTLJYBG9NsWt9krv487fHHMhXQNiCDiZGY' target='_blank'>ACES: History and Goals</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSXFtLqEHvPSfFFFFFFgGmzlRxua8OTic6WynoEwCoEiUoWyn6UL1bi3vlWpECi3-kJLq0tn' target='_blank'>ACES at-a-Glance</a>&nbsp;UIUC</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIeztg4kMv2wknwUupr-FYFrpJ67hC3ECjLId0435FfaWqoWPHeIlvFT0_WjMk5HRiYed6KzVMg35He3xe7gCHLeYN2fV_Ilo6bNe4RR2ek4-u2RARSs43ljY43' target='_blank'>Online Graduate Programs</a> UIUC</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzAvLJD7tVfSuuuuuuwV-Ek6c1JqgYsZ5EUr5Us62FeZgLIqbUnrMUFzX4DM51Wn6Gb138kj0nmGTXm0hNEYyc9aZoE01dED' target='_blank'>For Graduate Students</a> UIUC</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>农业与生物工程</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>7</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>$32,628</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>1月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>101</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>平均：3.6</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>秋季</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>IELTS要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>6.5</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>GRE要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>60%</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>GRE Subject</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>Not Required</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)(2)(3)</p><p>注：</p><p>（1）此处排名为<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/2020USNEWS美国生物农业工程排名' target='_blank'>2020USNEWS美国生物农业工程排名</a></p><p>（2）此处的GPA要求为奖学金平均成绩要求，具体请见项目设置*(1)</p><p>（3）GRE阅读占比50%，GRE写作占比50%，GRE数学占比80%*(1)</p><p>（4）该项目接受秋季和春季学期入学申请，截止日期分别为1月15日和10月1日*(1)</p><p>（5）IELTS单项要求均不低于6.0分；IELTS总分低于7.0分需参加ESL语言课程培训*(2)</p><p>（6）此处的学费是2016-17学年的学费信息，需要注意的是，该费用每年会有5%的涨幅*(3)</p><p><strong>项目设置</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:33.32%">			<p>项目名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:50.44%">			<p>项目英文名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p>GPA</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:33.32%">			<p>农业与生物工程硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:50.44%">			<p>MS in Agricultural and Biological Engineering</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p>3.0以上</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:33.32%">			<p>农业与生物工程博士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:50.44%">			<p>PhD in Agricultural and Biological Engineering</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.24%">			<p>3.25以上</p>			</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(1)</p><p><strong>申请说明</strong></p><p>伊利诺伊大学厄本那-香槟分校农业与生物工程系（Department of Agricultural and Biological Engineering，缩写ABE）主要分生物工程与农业工程两个专业方向，研究生招收MS与PhD学生。MS要求GPA不低于3.0，PhD要求GPA不低于3.25，通常获录取学生的GPA均高于上述最低要求，而获得奖学金的学生GPA一般不低于3.6。GRE分数要有两个：1）总分在60%以上；2）阅读与数学不低于80%，写作不低于50%。*(1)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>伊利诺伊大学厄本那-香槟分校农业与生物工程系开设的专业方向有：</p><ul>	<li>农业工程方向（Agricultural Engineering Concentration）	<ul>		<li>可再生能源系统（Renewable Energy Systems）</li>		<li>越野设备工程（Off-Road Equipment Engineering），如农用拖拉机、收割机等</li>		<li>土壤与水资源工程（Soil and Water Resources Engineering）</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><ul>	<li>生物环境工程方向（Bioenvironmental Engineering Concentration），也即生物工程方向	<ul>		<li>生态工程（Ecological Engineering）</li>		<li>食品与生物加工工程（Food and Bioprocess Engineering）</li>		<li>纳米生物工程（Nanoscale Biological Engineering）*(4)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=2rNMmQnVLQjzhEpaRRRRRRnsyVeFbmN18SvMuPWGd4KX-cKtjcepUyMo483rAmK3AZ5bWKlf3Kl7uOLy' target='_blank'>Graduate Programs</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=rrcuJRYZLDXYcz9nL3yzxRa34DM1r53-ujjExSFAhNZn7zvdYaJTQ1CAnDqz97pkI4P-ER3F9nclqzvHHO73VSQ6l9wNsxau-x2gnnWt9Oscuv3IwChG9ukZ' target='_blank'>Graduate Studies - Language Requirements</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCdswUvq6oesccccccGk-IyvSFdfji1Ow1_q-iJvpo9X6R9Xrm9vGo1O-BdOGVnbmn3bEnzkP7DNmL0FPwycewp' target='_blank'>2016-2017 Academic Year Graduate &amp; Professional Tuition Rates</a> UIUC</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_3kLbTirewxoooooo3Jz6PNndhKlupyO6tVxoVY5k1ClGwsm4VZxKV0xGVsNyku5TqS1xz7gwfYgxzoB' target='_blank'>Agricultural and Biological Engineering-Concentration</a> 伊利诺伊大学厄本那-香槟分校</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>农业与消费经济学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="wi