PhD/MD）</li></ul><p>硕士项目共计修读32个学分，博士项目共计修读64个学分。该系奖学金无需单独申请，自动随Offer发放。*(1)</p><p>注：人类发展与家庭研究仅开设博士学位。*(1)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>伊利诺伊大学厄本那-香槟分校人与社区发展系开设的专业领域有：</p><ul>	<li>儿童与青少年发展（Child and Adolescent Development in Context）</li>	<li>家庭背景差异、贫困与不平等及社会正义（Diverse Families, Poverty / Inequality, and Social Justice）</li>	<li>生命周期与健康和幸福（Health and Well-Being Across the Lifespan）</li>	<li>人际关系（Interpersonal / Intimate Relations）*(4)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=VrxbIdz2wjNSr1escccccgXl8PxjAN5cnPdhXWdl9bo_EGXwNHdfjJefVdNW3TJqOqN7y25RTsc_hSGXsGHgDp6NV94h1_F62QiZRetuuG4b6xhbq98ajny7FoIHtkA0hRj4UuCo_PFtlSIpQq1paJNBj9YiWvt5X' target='_blank'>Human and Community Development</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caRZLDXYczwZ3ERTkUwepxvQo7HrtKHp1Ud5-9UPgIdI1SJm6IU7PcSJRqpN7ybq43bACqHKqB3Z1Q9sTaWOEiCWsRS7KqGSGEcaJlTVAZywhSU' target='_blank'>Graduate Program Admissions Procedures</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWAXku1DPlHy000000o2fVzi5M7wx_kISk4pf_biam1nus1n-Q1iomkIfg7IoWzptkz2VGR5MOdXPDfxM_jnS_Y' target='_blank'>2016-2017 Academic Year Graduate &amp; Professional Tuition Rates</a> UIUC</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pS8L3NxwcPTaaaaaak5W_LntJEZx05VoBRX9HaWxsaW5vW5cT4SHqDvr4-qY8bz5tX3EFfrif_-tUZ5B1DlP_F-pXMauc1v7_kVEncjw' target='_blank'>Research Areas</a> UIUC</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>自然资源与环境</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>$26,502</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>1月1日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			