 Quality &amp; Biogeochemistry）*(4)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>学生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5ZdkfKZOFLJbbbbbxqH2fVzi5M7VMn0a1OS5oZxQXZxMRrEL0HbKyNtzDiqOZSu76WSZ3lBM4laZIlaKp--xDKibehgFsQR76iUlD1b5AcLaBNPOld_2KDFJZHbQZB6_RnqBTRlBTZGDYDcciByUfBJpvmu8SqaN' target='_blank'>2013 NRES Graduate Student Handbook</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYslWLs_unRZoBEssl7-gEBcchZCSpuKybmbLtgw9Seno6SpttIy4vLhyp4OHtKFru9WjtTP-Sf7KZgsKgSDuATiJLKtbZntWX' target='_blank'>How to Apply-NRES</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oEYkmG0lFOcEEEEEEih_T8SFaCoeBmpbm3t_BQSYAPXkvPOX0KPSiAmp_rCpiU8tgm8hgKDoVBQtkH3oJsbNbBn' target='_blank'>2016-2017 Academic Year Graduate &amp; Professional Tuition Rates</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=urKrNAm9wZUg37p5MMMMMM-rGEi7zKg_RD1_h-NPFFBH2iBH4bSiKEcskqNnPcQ9WTg3SuCIPsCDccLUPSLkHwmOT0M_TX5GxTYKIH' target='_blank'>Funding Information-NRES</a> UIUC</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhf1wcXfY2BI111111wtcI0SLn1fgJOmBQhLz70esL0ekY1OqzHMmKT625OS-QzZ1gpGt' target='_blank'>Research</a> UIUC</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>营养科学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>-</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>$26,502</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:18.02%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.38%">			<p>102以上</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.06%">			<p>3.0以上</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.4%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.74%">			<p>秋季、春季、夏季</p>			</td>	