artment of Kinesiology and Community Health，缩写KCH）主要分运动学、社区卫生两个专业方向，开设有以下学位项目：</p><ul>	<li>运动学硕士（Kinesiology Master of Science program）	<ul>		<li>生物行为运动学（Biobehavioral Kinesiology）</li>		<li>文化、教学与解说运动学（Cultural, Pedagogical, &amp; Interpretive Kinesiology）</li>		<li>运动生理学（Exercise Physiology）</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>运动学博士（Kinesiology Doctor of Philosophy program）</li>	<li>社区卫生硕士（Community Health Master of Science program）	<ul>		<li>卫生政策与管理方向（Specialization in Health Policy and Administration）</li>		<li>流行病学方向（Specialization in Epidemiology）</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>社区卫生博士（Community Health Doctor of Philosophy program）</li>	<li>公共卫生硕士（Master of Public Health,MPH）</li>	<li>康复硕士（M.S. in Rehabilitation）*(6)</li></ul><p>其中除MPH外，其余四个项目的申请时间、要求及方法等均相同：要求有GRE成绩，但无最低分数要求；绝大多数学生入学时均可获得一定形式的TA或RA奖学金资助，奖学金包括学费减免及工资补助等。*(6)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>运动学与社区卫生系TA奖学金申请表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aGR7wzOaRdN_PPPPPWq9cXoHl0-If359_j8x4b8xka8qFOhrqyQ4FzrZq1v4g3D-VMSJq3WrFOIwgzuEdTaKW1jte4aYwEOhxrW2K4G5vKQ0Bxlk7TV2cYlPs9' target='_blank'>Teaching Assistant Application</a>(pdf)</li>	<li>运动学与社区卫生系开设的研究领域与实验室：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2bLk7hGU12333333rDAUIk0fs6bNMD2tLYxlLYFv_MlQVbv5rXj05DgQvtwKmb' target='_blank'>RESEARCH GROUPS AND LABS</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNWtkO9fNTyHSSSSSSfImrY_M6VqBxTIHc3WLX3WiPH1iomkIfg7XtVP2NK42tQrioQBnxpgnzACiusmw-A4ifG' target='_blank'>How to Apply</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Trq48pWBwCpmL8xQTLGlpSOmAQ-gMWPdqdx-7mVvdTtl7iA1pzN_xuI9lZz0z5ppPYPOTW608k47zRx90u0lmFAhmcvWOOBdnYca6dJdt21T7LptOgWE4AuwvdtoUq' target='_blank'>Application Requirements</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjoEwgqXD4zDmmmmmm3hUvfrF2WuqRL70XkL_Pdx_-Oc0WzRSsklBsOADsORrsHlBVOcy-XSEKeRrBl2FnU2VEezv95cvKvT5' target='_blank'>KINESIOLOGY GRADUATE DEGREE PROGRAMS