每三年招生一次，下一次招生是2015年秋季</p><p>（2）戏剧历史评论PhD项目，本科生不能直接申请，需先拥有相关的硕士学位方可直接申请</p><p>（3）设计与制片MFA项目建议12月1日前申请*(2)(3)</p><p><strong>专业设置</strong></p><p>设计与制片MFA项目含以下专业分支：</p><ul>	<li>布景设计（Scenic Design）</li>	<li>布景技术（Scenic Technology）</li>	<li>服装设计（Costume Design）</li>	<li>服装技术（Costume Technology）</li>	<li>灯光设计（Lighting &amp; Media）</li>	<li>音箱设计（Sound Design）</li>	<li>舞台管理（Stage Management）</li>	<li>特效设计与管理（Properties Design &amp; Management）*(2)(3)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkMl0kiLYy5wFKTAzkBm5kh6xzfQR96sHAKZyRiM4Hz1D0Cav2PHTAeRRrK9xyM__gEqRcE2tPIwUeW5jaYaqqf6efs_cq' target='_blank'>Graduate Admission Process-Department of Theatre</a> UIUC</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJqweEscWmQzzzzzSD6CpP_C3uaHeP6-L5nCob7ZFvLUJcKMJaKLp0AnPIsgFxAg9xADGxlgPm3EBmoSGxbkRmbneI1_RwUgFxjcA4rjUlPdZi0d5MRFMm3Bn6JdNkrFZ6-RoOp' target='_blank'>Programs- Department of Theatre</a> UIUC</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=crr9MjoWw_8kImse88888Zn6mvLF-vhT26CdEusagHSTLAM5Abikxfpk7fjefrEUqYm3S78OC78j2uGpfwxYrL9yrdgMsFnqqy7ne8r4apGNBsDNB_VHYLsOGecsy_PTnPXxNqU_WQMvFajsFaH46' target='_blank'>Properties Design &amp; Management</a> UIUC</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>城市与区域规划</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.72%">			<p>开设学位</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.16%">			<p>MUP、PhD</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.1%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.46%">			<p>$27,652</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.1%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.46%">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:17.72%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:13.16%">			<p>102以上</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.1%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.46%">			<p>3.0以上</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.1%">			<p>可申请学期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:16.46%">			<p>秋季</p>			<